article.description: Chelsea Shine scored 15 points and Whitny Edwards added 14 points and 11 rebounds to lead Virginia (No. 11 ESPN/USA Today, No. 16 AP) to a 77-43 victory over Colorado on Monday night.
article.headline: Virginia outrebounds Colorado 68-43 in rout
article.story:
CHARLOTTESVILLE, Va. -- Chelsea Shine scored 15 points and Whitny Edwards added 14 points and 11 rebounds to lead Virginia (No. 11 ESPN/USA Today, No. 16 AP) to a 77-43 victory over Colorado on Monday night.

Monica Wright had 11 points and 10 rebounds and Aisha Mohammed scored 10 points to go with 14 rebounds for the Cavaliers (3-1), who outrebounded Colorado 68-43.

Virginia led by 10 at the half before using a 23-5 run in the second half to take a 56-29 lead on Edwards' jumper with 10:10 left in the game.

Kelly Jo Mullaney scored 10 points to lead the Buffaloes (2-1).
